{"tid":2283164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部澄清：港星建「旅遊氣泡」屬兩制下獨立決議 重申中方無意通關","createTime":"2020-11-12T11:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T16:38:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a848e889b33df33a2d1faa03d05ae1280543e503","tid":2283164,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"外交部：留意到港星旅遊氣泡 惟中方不主張開放境外旅遊<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部副部長羅照輝說，留意到香港及新加坡將會實行「旅遊氣泡」，強調中方並不否定「旅遊氣泡」，忘為是可以研究，但指當前情況下，境外旅遊應該要慎重，中方現在不主張開放境外旅遊，是相關主管部門的意見，但中方亦有與一些國家探討建立「綠色通道」及「快捷通道」網絡化，來推動人流及物流跨境往來及經濟恢復。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2365985&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BykBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=e74602f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365985</a>"},{"pid":"e087c06947696f9741c07a8e545795d7d759fbf5","tid":2283164,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935b3b10013c7b4394aaf81dd3d35e9bc3b4e876","tid":2283164,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad4e19111cf76d6633c9b4393ec2859fee7c1e1","tid":2283164,"uid":37596,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"兩制下有外交權咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4021eee23aa5728c7029dfbbbfdd2d9d5efc5e70","tid":2283164,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99072e2544ffb90c6b7da687884dcf2596a1eb2"